From 39dfbdceda3891f68b067103f5727f1cc1b596b0 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Alok Singh <aloksing@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Tue, 19 Aug 2025 13:54:10 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:DP:wifi:ath12k: Remove wifi7 related header from
 dp_mon.c

The ath12k monitor code currently includes headers related to Wi-Fi 7,
specifically `wifi7/hal_qcn9274.h`. These headers are not required for
common monitor mode functionality.

Removing wifi7/hal_qcn9274.h from dp_mon.c and Additionally,
the change addresses compilation issues that arose due to this
inclusion.

Move ath12k_dp_mon_rx_deliver, ath12k_dp_mon_rx_msdus_set_payload,
ath12k_dp_mon_rx_merg_msdus to dp_mon1.c because dual ring
specific chipsets never uses these functions.

Patch-dependency:
    0442-0001-UPSTREAM-DP-wifi-ath12k-Enable-non-compaction-on-qcn.patch

Signed-off-by: Alok Singh <aloksing@qti.qualcomm.com>
---
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp_mon.c      | 292 +-----------------
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/dp_mon.h      |   4 -
 drivers/net/wireless/ath/ath12k/hal_mon_cmn.h |  30 ++
 .../net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/dp_mon1.c   | 288 +++++++++++++++++
 .../net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hal_mon.c   |   6 +
 .../net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hal_mon.h   |  15 +-
 .../ath/ath12k/wifi7/hal_mon_qcn9274.c        |   8 +
 .../net/wireless/ath/ath12k/wifi7/hal_rx.h    |  10 -
 8 files changed, 343 insertions(+), 310 deletions(-)

